    (LP: #1743383)
    - [Packaging] git-ubuntu-log -- handle multiple bugs/cves better

  * Unable to handle kernel NULL pointer dereference at isci_task_abort_task
    (LP: #1726519)
    - Revert "scsi: libsas: allow async aborts"

