    - NFSv4: Fix up mirror allocation
    - xfs: XFS_IS_REALTIME_INODE() should be false if no rt device present
    - Linux 4.13.2

  * [Bug] Thunderbolt-patches: Related to the way the key for secure connection
    is handled (LP: #1717430)
